uk.co.caprica.vlcj.player

Class Logo

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.co.caprica.vlcj.player.Logo

  • public final class Logo
extends Object
    Builder for a Logo.

    Use like this, with a static import of logo(): 

       logo()
     .opacity(200)
     .location(100, 100)
     .file("logo.png")
     .enable()
     .apply(mediaPlayer)
   ;
